    Black Aracnia looks to Hibitchi, er, whatever and slams her heel down. 
"What dose this ship look like? A damn motel or something? AArgh!!!!!!!" She 
screamed, but then slowly took several deep breaths and readdresses the 
situation. "Alright, you may stay. Go find quarters and the things you need. 
But dont take advantage of us, Predacons dont like it." She said, being very 
cold hearted as she possibly could.

    Paralysis returned to the bridge and began to do the daily tasks and 
such. Eventually the others would join him.

    Black Aracnia entered the lab, and went directly to Darkmouse. "Well, how 
are you feeling? Can you get up and walk yet?"
